modules.description: Handles reading, writing, and manipulating text files line by line, including filtering, transforming, and concatenating lines. Operates on strings and lists of strings, with functions for line-by-line processing. Useful for parsing log files, processing configuration files, and preparing data for analysis.

Reads and writes files line by line, handling input and output channels directly. Processes strings and lists of strings, supporting operations like mapping, filtering, and folding over lines. Enables saving and restoring serialized values to and from files.
